<a name="创作背景" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">上瘾</span>创作背景</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="1" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">《上瘾 (Overdose)》是<a target=_blank href="/item/EXO">EXO</a>于2014年5月7日公开发行的第二张迷你专辑《上瘾 (Overdose)》的同名主打曲。歌曲分为两个版本，即<a target=_blank href="/item/EXO-M">EXO-M</a>的中文版本《上瘾 (Overdose)》以及<a target=_blank href="/item/EXO-K">EXO-K</a>的韩文版本《중독 (Overdose)》。由参与了<a target=_blank href="/item/Beyonce">Beyonce</a>,<a target=_blank href="/item/Chris%20Brown">Chris Brown</a>,<a target=_blank href="/item/Justin%20Timberlake">Justin Timberlake</a>等明星专辑制作的世界级团队The Underdogs和作曲家Kenzie合作创作，歌词讲述了男人深陷致命又强烈的爱情之毒无法自拔的故事，是一首以<a target=_blank href="/item/HipHop">HipHop</a>和<a target=_blank href="/item/R%26B">R&amp;B</a>为基础拥有Urban感觉的舞曲<sup>[1]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[1]_14797727">&nbsp;</a>
。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">EXO画上烟熏妆，展现与以往不同的神秘感，更值得注意的是，成员们再度挑战不同舞蹈风格，在预告中可以看到<a target=_blank href="/item/D.O.">D.O.</a>双脚支撑<a target=_blank href="/item/SUHO">SUHO</a>，<a target=_blank href="/item/KAI">KAI</a>和灿烈在一旁辅助，组成EXO的代表标示。而在中文版中则由<a target=_blank href="/item/XIUMIN">XIUMIN</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/LAY/13213073" data-lemmaid="13213073">LAY</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/CHEN">CHEN</a>和<a target=_blank href="/item/TAO/9699518" data-lemmaid="9699518">TAO</a>一起完成同样的高难度姿势。</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><div class="lemma-picture text-pic layout-center" style="width:500px; float: none; display: block; margin: 0px auto; clear: both;">
<a class="image-link" nslog-type="9317" 
			href="/pic/%E4%B8%8A%E7%98%BE/14919714/0/810a19d8bc3eb13590d28af6a51ea8d3fd1f4461?fr=lemma&ct=single" target="_blank"
		title="" style="width:500px;height:244px;">
<img  class="lazy-img" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAMAAAAoyzS7AAAAGXRFWHRTb2Z0d2FyZQBBZG9iZSBJbWFnZVJlYWR5ccllPAAAAAZQTFRF9fX1AAAA0VQI3QAAAAxJREFUeNpiYAAIMAAAAgABT21Z4QAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" data-src="https://gss3.bdstatic.com/-Po3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D500/sign=d8c45c9a35d12f2eca05ae607fc3d5ff/810a19d8bc3eb13590d28af6a51ea8d3fd1f4461.jpg"  alt="" style="width:500px;height:244px;"/>
</a>
</div></div><div class="anchor-list">
